---
description: Prefer systematic, tokenized solutions over one-off hacks
alwaysApply: true
---

When adding or changing features, prefer systematic approaches: design tokens, shared components, and clear data flow. Avoid ad hoc code, API drift, and one-off styling that bypasses the design system.

**Concrete UI and color rules:** see `.cursor/rules/design-system.mdc` and `AGENTS.md`.
